Sentencas: Yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolytes were deposited by suspension plasma spraying (SPS) and solution precursor plasma spraying (SPPS).
Titulo: Electrochemical performance of solid oxide fuel cells having electrolytes made by suspension and solution precursor plasma spraying

Sentencas: The electrolytes were evaluated for permeability, microstructure, and electrochemical performance.

Sentencas: With SPS, three different suspensions were tested to explore the influence of powder size distribution and liquid properties.
